{"tid":2181803,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局「復課但不面授」的政治盤算","createTime":"2020-08-31T00:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T04:05:58.000Z","uid":322378,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4f4f507a1256e641ef31714842db0b6cb8c77cf9","tid":2181803,"uid":322378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T00:20:25.000Z","msg":"聽日開學，教育局早前話學校可以如常復課，但唔可以現場授課，要透過網上授課。<br />\n當然係人都知網上上堂遠遠不及現場上堂，點解教育局又咁做？<br />\n其實好簡單，而家九成學校都用Zoom做網上授課，Zoom話就話美國公司，其實實際操作係大陸人！<br />\n好多學校已經課金Zoom最貴plan，大陸根本賺到盡，教育局根本就係利益輸送比大陸！"},{"pid":"ba07b153e8e7e5fa82c3a58b30be97d36259be26","tid":2181803,"uid":258192,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T00:21:33.000Z","msg":"其實可以用microsoft team"},{"pid":"83bbe3deecb48521a2dcd711b569275a884d62f1","tid":2181803,"uid":7708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T00:22:10.000Z","msg":"用緊google meet"},{"pid":"78d6c940890d0d68fb9ebed0877223ce995ec0f2","tid":2181803,"uid":322378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T00:22:46.000Z","msg":"要登入，好多學校怕麻煩"},{"pid":"cca9eabdfb79ef858faa438cab1203142e5ce4d1","tid":2181803,"uid":53970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ba07b153e8e7e5fa82c3a58b30be97d36259be26","tid":2181803,"uid":258192,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T00:21:33.000Z","msg":"其實可以用microsoft team"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T00:24:14.000Z","msg":"我都好奇點解Microsoft好似唔多食到呢條水咁 依家講親wfh就係zoom<br />\n定係其實zoom係疫情之前已經出左名"},{"pid":"56941748977cb8d083df47d6e505003925653141","tid":2181803,"uid":31827,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T00:27:10.000Z","msg":"過份解讀"},{"pid":"8afad1f0ac34fef53119d7c0c94eb5c4cb6d9254","tid":2181803,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cca9eabdfb79ef858faa438cab1203142e5ce4d1","tid":2181803,"uid":53970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ba07b153e8e7e5fa82c3a58b30be97d36259be26","tid":2181803,"ui